title: Updated Chic Community! High End Finishes!
posting_body: ['Newley renovated located in the heart of Grand Prairie, Texas, offering beautiful 1, 2, and 3 bedroom homes conveniently close to great services and fun activities within the Dallas-Fort Worth Metroplex.', 'We offer unique and well-planned apartment home designs, with a feeling of spaciousness and comfort.', 'Enjoy features such as designer white-on-white appliances, custom cabinets, decorative ceiling fans, elegant soaking tubs, oversized walk-in closets, 9-foot ceilings, crown molding, private balconies and patios, and more', 'Community Amenities', 'Reserved Covered Parking ($35)', 'Resort-style Swimming Pool', 'Outdoor Kitchen', 'Playground', 'Dog Park', 'Basketball Court', 'Firepit Lounge', 'BBQ/Picnic Area', 'Fitness Center', 'Entertainment Lounge', 'Gourmet Coffee Bar', 'Gated Access Community', 'Package Locker Room', 'Apartment Amenities....', "9' High Ceilings", 'Crown Molding in Living Room', 'Hardwood-style Flooring', 'Full-size Washer and Dryer Connections', 'Ceiling Fans in Master Bedroom*', 'Oversized Walk-in Closets', 'Elegant Soaking Tub with Shower', 'Extra Storage', 'Please Call Desiree with DASH Realty', 'show contact info', 'Mention Ad D-18']
